addCallback

public void addCallback(Callback c)
Install a callback to be invoked when the response is available.

If the response is already available when this method is called, the callback my be invoked in the calling thread immediately.

Parameters:
c - A runnable to be executed when a result is available. This will be called exactly once. The callback.execute(Result) method should execute quickly - under no circumstances should it ever block or perform any non-trivial tasks.
